column5: LOL no it's not the lottery but the next best thing, i belong to the north american fishing club for about 7 years now, filled out there live catch and release form and sent in a pick of a smallie i caught last year, editors picked 25 photo's from hundreds and had the club members vote on them, low and behold yesterday i get a registered letter saying i was  1 of the 10 lucky winners who won a $1000 fishing tackle package, i'm blown away!! i never have won anything in my life!I guess i better go out and buy a lottery ticket.
Nice one! Looks good on you.  Congratulations.
Thats about 5 lures worth.....     just kidding great news, if you need help carrying the tackle give me a call

Congrats on your win...  I've been a member for a long time...never entered any of their contests...used to receive the odd thing to field test but that stopped when I was brutally honest about the No-Knot fish hooks they sent for me to try...I think "piece of garbage " was part of my reply...
Fantastic, I have lots of extra storage if you need it
THAT'S great news lol Congrates!  If you need to get ride of all your old stuff, i'd be more then willing to "help" lolololololol  Post a copy of the winning photo if you have one.  -R-
Should probally receive it in 4 to 6 weeks if i'm lucky LOL. I will post some pic for sure.
Wow...$1000 bucks in equipment is great!  Congrats!
Now is that $1000 worth of tackle canadian or american?
Congrats! Hopefully its not alot of the stuff you already bought for the season.
